This is what he was like: His cheeks looked strange but his heart was strong; As a monster since childhood his magic was mighty.
A misshapen face that looked like a saddle; Eyes fiery bright with golden light.
His hairs were harder than needles of steel, And striking was the pattern of his tigerskin kilt.
