Once with his strength he fought heavenly kings, Putting a hundred and eight thousand warriors to flight.
His title was Great Sage Equaling Heaven; He was an expert with the gold−banded cudgel.
Today in the West he was using his powers To return to the cave and rescue Sanzang.
Journey to the West Watch Monkey as he stops his cloud and heads straight for the evil spirit's residence, where he found the gates under the gate towers shut.
