A great ramble of thunder could be heard, and there were sizzling flashes of lightning.
Indeed: The lightning was like snakes of purple gold; The thunder was like the noise of sleeping insects awakened.
Flashes of light like flying fire, Thunderclaps like landslides in the mountains.
