That will keep a proper distinction between the inner and outer quarters of the palace, and spare me from worrying.
I am going to sort this out to show my sincerity." The king accepted the suggestion and was boundlessly grateful.
He led the Tang Priest out of the inner quarters and straight to the throne hall.
All the queens and consorts returned to the inner palace.
A vegetarian meal was ordered while Pig and Friar Sand were sent for.
The two of them soon arrived.
