Be kind with your cudgel." When Monkey turned round he saw that it was the Star Lord of the Moon leading his beauties and immortals down on multicolored clouds to stand in front of him.
A flustered Monkey at once put his iron cudgel away, bowed and said, "Where are you going, Old Man?
