As I reckoned that she would be in mortal peril I have come here to save her life.
I do beg you, Great Sage, to spare her life out of consideration for me." Monkey assented, saying only, "I wouldn't dare harm her, I wouldn't dare.
No wonder she's so good with a medicine−pounding pestle. She's the Jade Hare.
