The only thing is that you mustn't let me go." On hearing this the prefect ordered, "Put the clamp on him first." The underlings then all fell on Monkey, fixed the clamp on his head, and tightened it so hard that the cord snapped with a twang.
The clamp was fastened, tightened and snapped with a twang again.
They did this three or four times, and the skin on his head was not even creased.
When they changed the cord and were tightening it again someone was heard coming in to report, "Your Honour, the Lord Assistant Protector Chen from the capital is coming.
